      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This vehicle is priced to move and ready for someone who doesn't mind a bit of a fixer-upper! While it shows significant signs of its time on the road and will definitely need some mechanical and cosmetic TLC, it offers a great entry point for a mechanic at heart or anyone looking for a very affordable start. It's an honest car with plenty of potential for the right owner!",
