    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a reliable vehicle in good condition, well-suited for daily use. The exterior paint still looks great, though there are some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light scratches consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing only minimal wear on the driver's seat bolster. It has been regularly serviced and runs smoothly, making it a solid choice for anyone looking for a dependable car.",
