      "description": "This vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a balance of performance and value. Meticulously maintained and showing pride of ownership, this unit delivers a refined driving experience with mechanical integrity you can depend on. It stands as a testament to quality engineering, offering a sophisticated aesthetic and reliable service for its next proprietor.",
