    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a high-gloss luster, though a close inspection reveals minor, typical road wear consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the seating surfaces are firm and free of tears, while the dashboard and touchpoints show minimal aging. Every feature, including the premium audio system and dual-zone climate control, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is responsive and quiet, backed by a consistent service record that includes a recent fluid flush and brake inspection. With deep tread on the tires and a smooth-shifting transmission, this car is fully prepared for its next chapter and requires no immediate maintenance.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
